			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">Custom Input Devices</span></h1>
			<div id="bodyContent">
				<div id="contentSub"><div id="mw-revision-info">Revision as of 05:23, 11 November 2014 by <a href="/User:Bob_Gneu" title="User:Bob Gneu" class="mw-userlink">Bob Gneu</a>  <span class="mw-usertoollinks">(<a href="/index.php?title=User_talk:Bob_Gneu&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="User talk:Bob Gneu (page does not exist)">Talk</a> | <a href="/Special:Contributions/Bob_Gneu" title="Special:Contributions/Bob Gneu">contribs</a>)</span></div><br />
